{"tid":1626083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「置頂」認真，今晚唔好出！屋企張床要人！","createTime":"2019-10-05T09:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T13:39:36.000Z","uid":126782,"like":11,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d23c5410d87226f66003aa5ae8683a918e9d518e","tid":1626083,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:41:54.000Z","msg":"我知好多人心有不甘 話惡法第一日實施 都唔上街<br />\n<br />\n但係你地認真諗下 佢今日全城戒嚴咁<br />\n<br />\n唔好講無黨鐵 係連7仔 超市 絕大部份商鋪都收檔<br />\n<br />\n如果今晚出 夜晚條街基本上除左手足 無其他人<br />\n<br />\n啲POPO可以見人就拉 一定中手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋政府叫曬全世界收鋪 營造一種白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n目的都係嚇走曬啲和理非同埋普通市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢就係為左短時間內捉曬勇武同魔法師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但放心 政府無可能日日叫啲鋪唔好做生意<br />\n<br />\n佢呢招無得日日用 我地只需要以逸待勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過左三個月 我諗大家都有共識唔會有Endgame<br />\n<br />\n今晚屋企張床要人 無謂送頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2336bbea512638af1a90f951036a8583c37eb9ae","tid":1626083,"uid":126782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:51:49.000Z","msg":"不服來辯 我只係唔想有手足被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabd61970abdb21d1f0d5bd65e62fc398c5bb765","tid":1626083,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:56:20.000Z","msg":"push 1/10"},{"pid":"d61be6d1fce430a8f24a658480fa52a05b4245ce","tid":1626083,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"Good afternoon sir，不推文回覆"},{"pid":"d60632be393f2572b88309ca44e86ce22333e01e","tid":1626083,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d61be6d1fce430a8f24a658480fa52a05b4245ce","tid":1626083,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"Good afternoon sir，不推文回覆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:11:14.000Z","msg":"笑 你推不推文回覆都推唔到架啦<br />\n<br />\n起左我底先啦 仲呀 Sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba4ebe500210545e97d1dd42d456c57c9f8b7a9","tid":1626083,"uid":55955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:11:48.000Z","msg":"條街不知幾多人"},{"pid":"7d587190d48ce27ada9f1d8f05e586e92ffc779c","tid":1626083,"uid":304663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:12:16.000Z","msg":"今晚屋企張床要人 無謂送頭！"},{"pid":"ccfc80ee9913245881ebb3328df40c517f6be1e3","tid":1626083,"uid":126782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ba4ebe500210545e97d1dd42d456c57c9f8b7a9","tid":1626083,"uid":55955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:11:48.000Z","msg":"條街不知幾多人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"D人散緊呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n最後再多人咪剩底手足<br />\n<br />\n咪俾人見一個拉一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解唔以逸待勞 叫佢白白封一晚<br />\n<br />\n聽日先一炮過"},{"pid":"ba8d98b4e11360b1d8703e402b607dfece16548d","tid":1626083,"uid":295340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:16:33.000Z","msg":"照你咁講咁佢營造氣氛都營造得幾失敗 全街都係人 車水馬龍"},{"pid":"c56bc986a4404f3471bb198b33c1c0d99f6123a1","tid":1626083,"uid":174775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"死on9"},{"pid":"6c663b29ad6b7490120266c151cb8ce751e6789d","tid":1626083,"uid":126782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba8d98b4e11360b1d8703e402b607dfece16548d","tid":1626083,"uid":295340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:16:33.000Z","msg":"照你咁講咁佢營造氣氛都營造得幾失敗 全街都係人 車水馬龍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"上面咪講啲人收緊曬工散緊<br />\n<br />\n我係叫啲勇武手足今晚唔好出姐<br />\n<br />\n連